text: Carl Fredrik af Wingård, born 26 September 1781 in Stockholm, Sweden, dead 19 September 1851 in Sunnersta, Sweden was a Swedish politician and Lutheran clergyman. He verved as the Church of Sweden Archbishop of Uppsala, between 1839 and 1851. == References == * Nordisk familjebok, article Wingård In Swedish Category:1781 births Category:1851 deaths Category:People from Stockholm Category:Archbishops of Uppsala
